  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3053621">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3053621/" class="title-link">自由的幻觉（自由感）是人信念上的支点</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3053621"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/cineNG/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1150841-21.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cineNG/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">西瓜籽丢了</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-03-09"
      class="main-meta">2010-03-09 12:20:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3053621_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  作者的行文不简洁，论证十分繁复啰嗦。关于自由意志，简单来说就是：所有对于自由意志存在的论证都漏洞百出，经不住推敲，实际上自由只是一种幻觉，尽管如此，这种幻觉仍有不可缺失的作用，因为人类需要为自己的存在找到自我能够接受的理由。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
